{"declarations":[{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Meta/Sym/Arith/Classify.html#Lean.Meta.Sym.Arith.classify?\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Meta</span>.<span class=\"name\">Sym</span>.<span class=\"name\">Arith</span>.<span class=\"name\">classify?</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">type</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.Expr\">Expr</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Sym/SymM.html#Lean.Meta.Sym.SymM\">SymM</a> <a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Sym/Arith/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Sym.Arith.ClassifyResult\">ClassifyResult</a></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Classify the algebraic structure of `type`, trying the strongest first:\nCommRing > Ring > CommSemiring > Semiring.\nResults are cached in `Arith.State.typeClassify`.\n","docLink":"./Lean/Meta/Sym/Arith/Classify.html#Lean.Meta.Sym.Arith.classify?","kind":"def","line":124,"name":"Lean.Meta.Sym.Arith.classify?","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Lean/Meta/Sym/Arith/Classify.lean#L124-L141"}}],"imports":["Init.Grind.Ring","Lean.Meta.DecLevel","Lean.Meta.Sym.Arith.EvalNum","Lean.Meta.Sym.Canon","Lean.Meta.Sym.SynthInstance"],"instances":[],"name":"Lean.Meta.Sym.Arith.Classify"}